==Russian==
===Etymology 1===
From [[ведать]] (''to [[know]]'', ''be [[in charge]]''), ultimately from PIE *woid-/*weid-/*wid- (''to [[see]]'', hence ''to [[know]]'').

====Noun====
'''ведение''' (védenije) {{n}}

# [[knowledge]], [[lore]]
# [[authority]], [[charge]], [[competence]]

=====Alternate spellings=====
*{{Unicode|[[вѣдѣніе]]}} (védenije, ''pre-1918'')

